node.text:
WE ARE DEALING WITH A PANDEMIC
AND ITS NOT FUN
.
.
Dealing with a pandemic is maybe one of THE lifetime events you are going through right now and the adverse effects of this may extend in next quiet a few decades or more
.
So during this quarantine period

If you are stressing out 
If you cannot be productive
If you cannot pursue any of your hidden hobbies
If you havent made a fancy ass cake yet
If you havent started working out
If you are feeling low and demotivated
If you are not making the best use of your time

Always remember
IT IS ABSOLUTELY FINE‚ù§Ô∏è
.
It is a pandemic we are dealing with, not some creativity or fitness competition where you need to prove that you are making the best use of your time during quarantine.
.
Rather what should be your outlook during the quarantine time
* Stay healthy
* Maintain socialdistancing
* Wear your masks
* Eat healthy and boost your immunity
* Do whatever makes you happy
* Avoid any person/news that spread rumor/negativity
#pandemic #covid19 #quarantinelife

node.text: To everyone reading this: whatever happens to you, please don't give up on love. Maybe you don't need the whole world to love you. Maybe you just need one person. Sometimes, two people have to fall apart to realize how much they need to fall back together. When you realize you want to spend the rest of your life with somebody, you want the rest of your life to start as soon as possible. So don't give up on your love. Love didn't hurt you. The wrong person hurt you. Remember, the best and most beautiful things in the world cannot be seen or even heard, but must be felt with the heart.

node.text:
Tahukah Ayah Bunda?
Ikatan Dokter Anak Indonesia (IDAI) merekomendasikan vaksin influenza sejak anak usia 6 bulan sampai 18 tahun. Perhimpunan Dokter Spesialis Penyakit Dalam Indonesia (PAPDI) juga merekomendasikan pemberian vaksin flu setiap tahun nya pada semua kelompok usia.
Vaksin Influenza memang tidak dapat mencegah COVID 19, namun dapat melindungi dari penyakit flu yang memiliki gejala mirip dengan COVID 19. Sehingga membantu menjaga sistem pernafasan terhadap penyakit infeksi saluran nafas & mengurangi risiko mengalami gejala yang memiliki kerancuan dengan COVID 19.
Sudahkah Ayah Bunda, serta anggota keluarga lain mendapatkan vaksin influenza tahun ini?
Yuk jadwalkan vaksin Influenza bagi Anak, Orang Tua, dan Keluarga di rumah. üòä

node.text:
Angka kasus positif COVID-19 di Indonesia saat ini terbilang sangat tinggi, mencapai 3 ribu kasus positif per harinya. Melonjaknya angka itu disinyalir karena berbagai pelonggaran sebelumnya. Pemerintah dikritik terlalu mementingkan ekonomi.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
Untuk itu, Ketua DPR Puan Maharani berharap pemerintah melakukan evaluasi terkait penanganan pandemi COVID-19 serta dampak yang menyertainya. Menurutnya, pemerintah harus mengutamakan keselamatan dan kesehatan masyarakat dalam menangani pandemi tersebut.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
"Saat ini adalah saat krusial bagi pemerintah untuk bergotong royong bersama DPR RI, untuk mengevaluasi. Kalau memang saat ini adalah waktu untuk kita menginjak rem, jangan mempercepat laju dari apa yang menjadi keinginan kita," kata Puan, usai rapat paripurna di DPR, Jakarta, Selasa 1 September 2020.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
Puan mengatakan, keselamatan dan kesehatan masyarakat serta petugas medis harus diutamakan. Jangan sampai pemerintah melakukan pembiaran terhadap kondisi saat ini. Termasuk demi alasan ekonomi.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
Terlebih, tenaga medis sudah banyak berguguran. Ikatan Dokter Indonesia (IDI) mencatat, sudah ada 100 dokter yang gugur akibat mengurus pandemi ini dan mereka juga ikut terjangkit.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
"Sudah waktunya pemerintah mengetatkan protokol COVID-19 agar masyarakat kembali waspada, penting menjaga kesehatan diri, lingkungan, dan masyarakat," ujarnya.‚†Ä
===‚†Ä
Presiden Joko Widodo mengungkapkan, peningkatan kasus Virus Corona atau COVID-19 di Tanah Air masih tergolong relatif lebih baik ketimbang negara lain. Namun ia mengingatkan, agar tetap hati-hati mengingat angka kematian terus meningkat.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
Selain di Asia, Jokowo membandingkan dengan kasus Corona di Eropa.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
"Di negara kita walaupun ada peningkatan di beberapa daerah, tapi kalau dibandingkan negara lain, posisi Indonesia masih relatif terkendali," kata Jokowi di Istana Kepresidenan Bogor, Jawa Barat, Selasa, 1 September 2020.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
Jokowi bilang, meski angka kematian sudah menurun menjadi 4,2 persen dari sebelumnya 7,83 persen, jumlah itu tak bisa dianggap remeh. Karena angka fatality rate di negara kita masih lebih tinggi daripada fatality rate global 3,36 persen.‚†Ä
===‚†Ä
#vivacoid #jokowi #puanmaharani #coronavirus #covid19 #ekonomi

node.text:
Hi , I am Dr Rohan Sawant. I have completed my MBBS from Terna Medical College, Navi Mumbai and MD in RadioDiagnosis from D Y Patil Hospital & Research Centre, Navi Mumbai. 
After my post graduation I was working in Apollo Hospitals, Navi Mumbai and D Y Patil Hospital, Navi Mumbai. 
Radiology is a diverse stream in it self but during my work I could figure out my interest towards fetal medicine, after which I went towards the super speciality fellowship of fetal medicine under one of the best fetal medicine expert of Asia Dr. Nitin Chaubal. 
Last few months left of my training after which I m really eager to serve for the life which grows inside the mother’s womb.
.

SDRA por #covid19 √© SDRA: ficou redundante discutir isso. Neste estudos, os pacientes dos dois grupos (SDRA porCOVID-19 e SDRA n√£o-COVID) foram submetidos √† manobra de recrutamento alveolar (LRM) com incremento de PEEP de 25 a 40 cmH20 por 2 minutos em cada step, mantendo delta de press√£o de 15 cmH20. Definiram resposta √† LRM como aumento da PaO2/FiO2 de 20% nas primeiras 2-4 horas p√≥s LRM. Todos os pacientes, nos dois grupos, mantiveram ventila√ß√£o protetora. 68% dos pacientes tamb√©m receberam posi√ß√£o prona. Em geral, a complac√™ncia do sistema respirat√≥rio em m√©dia foi 30ml/cmH20 e n√£o diferiu significativamente entre os dois grupos. 63% dos pacientes no grupo COVID19 e 72% no grupo n√£o COVID-19 responderam com melhora da oxigena√ß√£o √† LRM. Quanto √† posi√ß√£o prona, a taxa de resposta foi maior: 82% vs 91%, respectivamente. N√£o houve diferen√ßa estatisticamente significativa em nenhuma das vari√°veis avaliadas. Os autores fazem uma discuss√£o interessante: “Nossos resultados mostraram que as principais caracter√≠sticas das medidas de press√£o e da mec√¢nica respirat√≥ria (como press√£o de plat√¥, Driving Pressure e complac√™ncia do sistema respirat√≥rio) n√£o diferiram significativamente quando comparamos a SDRA COVID-19 ou n√£o-COVID-19.  No geral, a complac√™ncia m√©dia do sistema respirat√≥rio [IQR] foi de 30 [23-40] mL / cmH2O;  os dois grupos n√£o diferiram significativamente a este respeito.  Esse valor est√° pr√≥ximo aos relatados na literatura para SDRA COVID-19 e n√£o COVID-19. Nossos resultados v√£o contra as suposi√ß√µes feitas inicialmente por muitos m√©dicos (inclusive n√≥s), segundo as quais a mec√¢nica pulmonar na SDRA com COVID-19 n√£o √© afetada, mas as trocas gasosas s√£o mais gravemente prejudicadas do que na SDRA n√£o COVID-19. Definiram resposta √† LRM como aumento da PaO2/FiO2 de 20% nas primeiras 2-4 horas p√≥s LRM. Todos os pacientes, nos dois grupos, mantiveram ventila√ß√£o protetora. 68% dos pacientes tamb√©m receberam posi√ß√£o prona. Em geral, a complac√™ncia do sistema respirat√≥rio em m√©dia foi 30ml/cmH20 e n√£o diferiu significativamente entre os dois grupos. 63% dos pacientes no grupo COVID19 e 72% no grupo n√£o COVID-19 responderam com melhora da oxigena√ß√£o √† LRM. Quanto √† posi√ß√£o prona, a taxa de resposta foi maior: 82% vs 91%, respectivamente. N√£o houve diferen√ßa estatisticamente significativa em nenhuma das vari√°veis avaliadas. Os autores fazem uma discuss√£o interessante: “Nossos resultados mostraram que as principais caracter√≠sticas das medidas de press√£o e da mec√¢nica respirat√≥ria (como press√£o de plat√¥, Driving Pressure e complac√™ncia do sistema respirat√≥rio) n√£o diferiram significativamente quando comparamos a SDRA COVID-19 ou n√£o-COVID-19.  No geral, a complac√™ncia m√©dia do sistema respirat√≥rio [IQR] foi de 30 [23-40] mL / cmH2O;  os dois grupos n√£o diferiram significativamente a este respeito.  Esse valor est√° pr√≥ximo aos relatados na literatura para SDRA COVID-19 e n√£o COVID-19. Nossos resultados v√£o contra as suposi√ß√µes feitas inicialmente por muitos m√©dicos (inclusive n√≥s), segundo as quais a mec√¢nica pulmonar na SDRA com COVID-19 n√£o √© afetada, mas as trocas gasosas s√£o mais gravemente prejudicadas do que na SDRA n√£o COVID-19. Na verdade, nossos resultados sugerem que a dissocia√ß√£o entre a mec√¢nica pulmonar e as trocas gasosas n√£o √© maior na SDRA com COVID-19 do que na SDRA n√£o COVID-19.  Em contraste, observamos diferen√ßas significativas no padr√£o de envolvimento da tomografia computadorizada de t√≥rax: opacidade difusa em vidro fosco foi mais frequente na SDRA de COVID-19, enquanto derrame pleural foi menos frequente.”

How was your September 1st? 

It was a crazy whirlwind of emotions for me. Had so much time with these two munchkins over the past few months. 2020 has really given us time together that I’ll forever treasure. This is also the first time both of my girlies will be immersed into Hebrew speaking ganim üôàThat’s probably the hardest part for us. Because I can’t take them in and spend the time to make sure they’re ok the way I would have liked (Thanks #covid19 ) and I can’t be there translating and double checking that everything is ok. It’s really hard to let go and give someone else control of my most precious gems. 

But these kids have proven to be resilient time and time again. And they impress me with their abilities every single day. Wishing all you worried mamas much calm and a happy and healthy year to all your little munchkins. I’ll just be here with my box of tissues üò≠

node.text:
..
.
Entahlah...üòëüòëüòë
.
Presiden Joko Widodo menyebut kondisi COVID-19 di Indonesia masih relatif terkendali. Ia mengingatkan kepala daerah yang angka kasus positif di daerahnya masih tinggi untuk berhati-hati.⁣
⁣
"Kalau dibandingkan dengan negara-negara lain posisi Indonesia masih relatif terkendali, dan ini yang harus kita jaga, bahwa pengendalian manajemen untuk COVID betul-betul masih pada posisi terkendali,” ucap Jokowi saat memberikan pengarahan kepada gubernur se-Indonesia di Istana Bogor, Selasa (1/9/2020).⁣
⁣
Meski @Jokowi menyebut tren COVID-19 di Indonesia terkendali, data Satgas penanggulangan COVID-19 menujukkan beberapa rumah sakit rujukan COVID-19 mulai kehabisan tempat tidur. Per Senin (31/8/2020) kemarin, tingkat keterisian ICU dan ruang isolasi di 67 rumah sakit rujukan di DKI Jakarta sudah jauh di atas standar WHO.⁣
⁣
WHO mematok angka ideal tingkat keterisian rumah sakit di bawah 60%. Namun, tingkat keterisian ruang isolasi di 67 rumah sakit DKI mencapai 69%, sedangkan tingkat keterisian ruang isolasi sebesar 77%.⁣
⁣
“Kondisi ini memang kondisi yang tidak ideal. Pemerintah sedang mendorong menurunkan angka keterpakaian tempat tidur ini untuk bisa di bawah 60%,” ucap Juru Bicara Satgas Penanggulangan COVID-19, Wiku Adisasmito, kemarin.⁣
⁣
Tingginya angka keterisian ini juga tak diimbangi penambahan tenaga kesehatan dan dokter. Bahkan, jumlah dokter yang meninggal malah terus bertambah dan tercatat lebih dari 100 orang per kemarin.⁣
⁣
Sementara itu, kasus positif di Indonesia juga masih dilaporkan mengalami kenaikan. Per hari ini, Selasa (1/9/2020), kasus konfirmasi positif bertambah 2.775, sehingga total kasus positif mencapai 177.571. Penambahan juga terjadi pada pasien sembuh yakni 2.098 orang, sehingga total pasien sembuh mencapai 128.057. Adapun pasien yang meninggal dalam sehari bertambah 88 orang, sehingga total kasus meninggal di Indonesia mencapai 7.505 orang.⁣
⁣

Hai fashion people! Semangat Giambattista Valli untuk mendandani wanita adalah yang kedua setelah kecintaannya pada bunga yang indah. Musim ini dia menggabungkan keduanya. Beberapa anggrek yang baru dipotong bahkan diaplikasikan pada wajah para model, membingkai matanya dengan kelopak kuning dan putih yang lembut. El contacto con otras personas, superficies y objetos a lo largo del d√≠a hace que se acumulen g√©rmenes en las manos. En general, lo mejor es lavarse las manos con agua y jab√≥n. Los jabones antibacterianos de venta libre no son m√°s efectivos para matar g√©rmenes que el jab√≥n com√∫n.

Nesses momentos √© o nosso Ser querendo algo mais que nos fa√ßa sentir como existindo e fazendo parte da nossa hist√≥ria como autor, onde nossas escolhas s√£o as que podemos fazer no momento, mas assumindo cada uma delas com consci√™ncia, sem buscar culpados pelo o que nos acontece. 
Viver plenamente cada momento, de dor ou de alegria, de falta ou abundancia, de Covid19 e isolamento. Mas de uma forma que possa me olhar no fundo do meu ser e para as pessoas que est√£o ao meu redor na longa ou curta caminhada na vida, e responder se n√£o todas, pelo menos uma das perguntas que me surge √† cabe√ßa, s√≥ que para isso eu preciso estar ciente que confrontarei as sombras internas que me impedem de dar o pr√≥ximo passo.

node.text:
Dear, Travelers

Tidak terasa 6 bulan kita telah lewati sejak kasus #covid19 pertama terjadi di Indonesia dan kita semua dihadapkan pada situasi yang tidak mudah dan perlu untuk melakukan anjuran dari pemerintah seperti #dirumahaja dan #workfromhome.

Di masa #newnormal atau #adaptasikebiasaanbaru ini, Mogens Guest House telah beroperasi kembali dengan mengutamakan keamanan, kebersihan dan kenyamanan bagi setiap tamu.
Kami telah melakukan upaya pencegahan penyebaran COVID-19 diseluruh area penginapan baik area umum maupun kamar tamu.

Kami harap kita semua bisa turut serta mendukung pemerintah dalam mencegah penyebaran COVID-19di masyarakat.
Mari tetap produktif dan juga tidak perlu ragu untuk #kembaliliburan dengan tetap waspada, jaga jarak, jaga kebersihan pribadi.
Kita berharap masa pandemi ini bisa segera kita lewati bersama!

Terima kasih bagi para #sobatmogens yang telah memilih Mogens Guest House sebagai tempat singgahmu selama di Bandung.

Mie koclok merupakan mie basah yang disiram kuah kental putih yang gurih dan sebagai pelengkapnya telor  rebus dan juga suwiran ayam plus bawang goreng dihidangkan.. Membuat rasa hidangan satu ini #nganggenin banget. ü•∞ü•∞ü•∞
-
Dan.. Kebetulan istri saya salah satu pecinta dari #kulinerkhascirebon ini. Namun cukup lama sudah belum menjamah nya... Karena efek pandemi #covid19 yang merajalela... Namun akhirnya.. Kami memutuskan.. Tiba saat nya menikmati kuliner satu ini... Tentu nya dengan memperhatikan protokol kesehatan ketika menyantapnya.
-
Jadi.. Ketika bermain di kota cirebon?? Ini salah satu kuliner yang wajib banget untuk dijajal di kota ini
-

Ciascuno di noi ha potuto constatare dai dati, dalle notizie di livello scientifico che seguire le norme √® fondamentantale per sconfiggere il Coronavirus e riprendere le nostre vite di sempre. 

Vi invito ad installare l’app #IMMUNI (la potete scaricare qui https://www.immuni.italia.it/), utile supporto qualora fossimo entrati a contatto ravvicinato con una persona positiva. 
Dobbiamo eliminare definitivamente questa epidemia dalla nostra vita e ognuno di noi deve fare la sua parte.

node.text:
“Businesses of all natures have taken real measures to step up to make the town safe.”

That was the key take out for Cllr Kevin Jenkins, Worthing’s Executive Member for Regeneration following his town centre walkabout when he chatted to local traders about the measures they’ve put in place to welcome back their customers. 

Starting off in Montague Street West, Cllr Jenkins popped into a long-standing local business, @greenfingersflorist. They’ve been in Worthing since 1987. He then headed to Bath Place to visit one of Worthing’s best known shops @ilovecandyworthing before popping into the cafe next door, @bungaroosh_cafebistro. 

Next on his route was Montague Quarter to visit the football paraphernalia shop, Saturday 3pm. They recently moved from The Royal Arcade to their new premises, Cllr Jenkins’ final visit was to welcome start-up business, @lucifersbar in Portland Road to Worthing.

“There’s a real air of confidence to come into the town,” says Cllr Jenkins, who praises Worthing for its mix of cafes, restaurants and independent shops. “It’s time to come back and enjoy our town again.”

#Worthing #business #businessowner #safetyfirst #flowers #candy #food #football #covid19

T√ºm T√ºrkiye’de olduƒüu gibi Kars’ta da koronavir√ºs vaka sayƒ±sƒ±nda artƒ±≈ü g√∂zleniyor. Peki Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ± tarafƒ±ndan yetkilendirilen Kafkas √úniversitesi (KA√ú) Tƒ±p Fak√ºltesi ve Saƒülƒ±k Ara≈ütƒ±rma ve Uygulama Hastanesi’nde ka√ß ki≈üiye koronavir√ºs testi yapƒ±ldƒ±?

Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ± T√ºrkiye’de de hƒ±zla yayƒ±lmaya devam eden Kovid-19 kaynaklƒ± enfeksiyonlarƒ±n tanƒ±sƒ±nƒ±n koyabileceƒüi aralarƒ±nda Kafkas √úniversitesi Tƒ±p Fak√ºltesi ve Saƒülƒ±k Ara≈ütƒ±rma ve Uygulama Hastanesi’nin de bulunduƒüu 223 merkezi yetkilendirdi.

KA√ú Tƒ±p Fak√ºltesi Uygulama Ara≈ütƒ±rma Hastanesi Mikrobiyoloji Laboratuvarƒ±nda ger√ßekle≈ütirilen real time PCR testi hakkƒ±nda a√ßƒ±klama yapan Kafkas √úniversitesi Tƒ±p Fak√ºltesi ve Saƒülƒ±k Ara≈ütƒ±rma ve Uygulama Hastanesi Ba≈ühekimi Prof. Dr. Sinan Kocat√ºrk, “1 Nisan 2020 tarihinde √ºniversitemiz PCR testiyle ile ilgili olarak Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ± tarafƒ±ndan yetkilendirme belgesi aldƒ±. Bu tarih itibariyle biz de testlerimize ba≈üladƒ±k. Sadece Kars i√ßinde deƒüil aynƒ± zamanda Iƒüdƒ±r ve Ardahan gibi, hatta Artvin’e kadar uzanan bir b√∂lgede testler yapƒ±lƒ±yor. 1 Nisan’dan bug√ºne kadar merkezimizde 37 bin 250 PCR testi yapƒ±ldƒ± ve bunlarƒ±n sonu√ßlarƒ± Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ±na bildirildi, oradan da ƒ∞l Saƒülƒ±k M√ºd√ºrl√ºkleriyle payla≈üƒ±ldƒ±. Son 15 g√ºne kadar bu ≈üekilde giden √ßalƒ±≈üma, Iƒüdƒ±r’da PCR testi yapƒ±lmasƒ±yla merkezimizde Ardahan ve Kars’a hizmet veremeye ba≈üladƒ±k.” dedi.

Kocat√ºrk, Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ± genelgelerine uygun olarak hem hasta takibi hem de PCR test yapƒ±mƒ±nƒ±n devam ettiƒüini belirterek, “Son zamanlarda Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ±nƒ±n g√ºnl√ºk √ºlkede 100 binin √ºzerine √ßƒ±kan test sayƒ±sƒ±yla bizim de g√ºnl√ºk test sayƒ± oranƒ±mƒ±z 700-800, bazen binli rakamlara kadar √ßƒ±kabildiƒüi g√ºnler oluyor. Bu konuda personelimiz 24 saat testleri doƒüru ≈üekilde yapmak i√ßin gayret g√∂steriyor. ≈ûuanda bu ≈üekilde bir y√∂ntem izliyoruz, Saƒülƒ±k Bakanlƒ±ƒüƒ± genelgelerine uygun olarak hem hasta takibi hem de PCR test yapƒ±mƒ± devam ediyor.” ifadesini kullandƒ±.

node.text:
Unprecedented times calls for the ‘joining of hands’ across agencies, tapping on the strengths and expertise of our CBRNE team. All hands on deck for our scientists, to run tests on swab samples timely and efficiently to secure our borders against #COVID19. In fact, their tireless work continues regardless of a pandemic as the effort involved in countering CBRNE threats and hazards happens round-the-clock! Find out more from the perspective of our young CBRNE scientist via the link in our bio.

• Repost @mhasingapore “The swab test operation at our air, land and sea checkpoints was a multi-agency effort. The CBRNE team’s task was to run tests on the swab samples to detect and identify travellers who had COVID-19 quickly, so that they could receive treatment. This also helped to curb the spread of the virus in the community.” – Ms May Ong, Director, Chemical, Biological, Radiological, Nuclear and Explosives (CBRNE), @htxsg 
.

node.text:
Where did summer go? üò¢
.
.
This September and back-to-school season is quite unlike any other (to say the least) & this post goes out to everyone who is feeling uneasy/unsure about what’s ahead. You can do it. It sounds lame but its true!¬†¬†It can be so much easier to doubt yourself, but doubting yourself will never get you anywhere.
.
.
Sadly Covid isnt going anywhere anytime soon, so step up to the challenge, adapt, learn & grow. Most importantly don’t forget to reach out to your support systems (myself included). You aren’t expected to deal with everything on your own & it’s normal to feel like things are out of your control, BUT it’s not ok to start doubting yourself and neglecting self-care.
.
.

(2/3) I came to this town in 1980 to help my nephew, a herbal and spiritual healer. When my nephew died six years ago, the gods passed down his knowledge to me. I gained experience in plant-based remedies for common ailments and spiritual attacks. These remedies have proven successful, and my customers can attest to this. When patients come here for healing, I seek guidance from the gods and ancestors, and they always show me what to do. ⁠
⁠
Je suis venu dans cette ville en 1980 pour aider mon neveu, un gu√©risseur √† base de plantes et de spiritualit√©. Lorsque mon neveu est mort il y a six ans, les dieux m'ont transmis son savoir. J'ai acquis de l'exp√©rience dans les rem√®des √† base de plantes pour les maux courants et les attaques rituelles. Ces rem√®des ont fait leurs preuves, et mes clients peuvent en t√©moigner. Lorsque des patients viennent ici pour se faire soigner, je demande conseil aux dieux et aux anc√™tres, et ils me montrent toujours ce qu'il faut faire. ⁠
⁠

node.text:
(1/3) God is punishing humanity with this virus. The Europeans are relying on human intelligence instead of wisdom from God. This pandemic, just like others before, should remind us that we don't know everything. We should always look up to the Supreme Being. Honestly, I have not prayed about a remedy for the coronavirus disease, and it's because I haven't seen anyone with the virus. I have been following the news, and I wear my mask whenever I am going out to protect myself. There is no reason to be overzealous when I can save my life by following the laid-out health guidelines. ⁠
⁠
Dieu punit l'humanit√© avec ce virus. Les Europ√©ens s'appuient sur l'intelligence humaine plut√¥t que sur la sagesse de Dieu. Cette pand√©mie, comme d'autres avant elle, devrait nous rappeler que nous ne savons pas tout. Nous devrions toujours lever les yeux vers l'√ätre supr√™me. Honn√™tement, je n'ai pas pri√© pour un rem√®de contre la maladie du coronavirus, et c'est parce que je n'ai vu personne avec le virus. J'ai suivi les nouvelles, et je porte mon masque chaque fois que je sors pour me prot√©ger. Il n'y a aucune raison d'√™tre trop z√©l√© alors que je peux sauver ma vie en suivant les directives sanitaires √©tablies. ⁠
⁠

Influencia de los factores gen√©ticos en la respuesta a tratamientos para COVID-19.

Desde el inicio de la pandemia de COVID-19 diferentes estudios han evaluado la posibilidad de que la composici√≥n gen√©tica de una persona influya en si ser√° m√°s o menos susceptible a la infecci√≥n por el coronavirus SARS-CoV-2. Mientras este tema sigue en investigaci√≥n, un reciente estudio de la Universidad de Minnesota acaba de abordar otra cuesti√≥n que podr√≠a ser tambi√©n muy relevante para hacer frente a la infecci√≥n del virus: ¬øpueden influir los genes en la respuesta a las terapias farmacol√≥gicas que van surgiendo como candidatas para tratar la COVID-19?

Los investigadores de la Universidad de Minnesota reportan la existencia de m√∫ltiples variantes gen√©ticas que influyen en c√≥mo se metabolizan algunos de los f√°rmacos candidatos para COVID-19 lo que podr√≠a influir en la respuesta de los pacientes a los tratamientos. Estos resultados les llevan a se√±alar como recomendable realizar estudios farmacogen√©ticos que eval√∫en si la variaci√≥n gen√©tica de una persona puede influir en su respuesta a los tratamientos para COVID-19. La urgencia de la situaci√≥n actual no ha permitido hasta el momento evaluar esta posibilidad, ni su aplicabilidad en el √°mbito cl√≠nico.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Songadh The Perfect Town üñ§ on September 01, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'a Appearing for JEE/NEET? RSS IS ORGANIZING FREE TRANSPORT, food and financial aid for students while ABVP launches helpline In an effort to help the students appearing for exams across the country, nationwide aid is being provided by the two organizations in order to ease the pressure from students who are facing difficulties.'.
Photo by Songadh The Perfect Town üñ§ on September 01, 2020.

node.text:
While the Modi government is facing heat after their decision to not postpone/cancel the national exams despite COVID19 shere over 26 lakh students are supposed to appear, RSS and ABVP members have come forward to provide all possible aid to the students.

From free transport to free food and even financial aid to students who’re facing cash crunch amid the pandemic, the Rashtriya Swamsewak Sangh (RSS) has activated all its local units and asked to keep an eye on the situation so that they can officially launch the campaign.

“In several areas due to flooding, students are finding it difficult to travel. Our local units are helping them,” said the senior RSS functionary.

“Several students had gone back to their villages or towns due to the lockdown; we are helping them too. At the same time, if there are issues related to lack of funds, our units are even taking care of that.”

Most of the local units that are carrying out this work are in flood-affected areas of Bihar, Madhya Pradesh, Maharashtra, West Bengal and Gujarat among others.

In order to contact RSS, all you have to do is reach to your nearest shakha (details will be texted to you via online free membership/registration)

Although all the SOPs are being followed at the examination centres allotted by the government (as per visuals), these measures by RSS and ABVP will help curb the potential threat of virus spread.

On the other hand, Akhil Bhartiya Vidyarthi Parishad (ABVP), a student organization has issued nationwide helpline for students of every state so that in case of any difficulty/emergency, the members of the organization can aid them.

Several opposition parties and student unions have although opposed the holding of the exams, accusing the Modi government of putting students at risk amidst the pandemic and demanded the postponement of the two exams.

The National Testing Agency (NTA) will conduct JEE Main 2020 between 1 September and 6 September while the National Entrance Cum Eligibility Test (NEET) is scheduled to be held on 13 September.

For more, visit website (link in bio)
.

node.text:
Michelle Donelan, Minister of State for Universities in the UK, talks about how, despite the current difficulties COVID-19 has presented to international students, you are welcome here.

And don’t forget, UK degrees are of a high standard and are internationally valuable whatever form they take – whether they are delivered in person or online.

There’s still time to apply for a course that begins in September, or you may like to wait until our January course start dates. Either way, don’t let COVID-19 delay your study plans and success.

node.text:
Post di @niccoemamma_nutricion
L'attuale pandemia causata dal coronavirus ha generato vari problemi a livello mondiale di tipo sanitario, sociale, economico e tanti altri. Tuttavia, alla gravit√† dei suddetti problemi si aggiunge anche una cattiva alimentazione e la presenza di malattie non trasmissibili (MNT) come il diabete mellito, l’obesit√† e le malattie cardiovascolari. Queste condizioni sono caratterizzate da un’infiammazione sistemica che pu√≤ essere una particolarit√† comune di queste malattie, che influisce sugli esiti dei pazienti contro COVID 19.
Studi recenti, sembrano dimostrare che le persone con MNT e infettati da COVID 19 hanno avuto una prognosi peggiore nello sviluppo della malattia durante il ricovero in ospedale.
¬†Alcuni studi dimostrano che adottando misure per migliorare i fattori di rischio modificabili come la dieta, l’esercizio e uno stile di vita salutare, si potrebbe generare un effetto protettivo nelle persone. ¬†
Ci√≤ significherebbe riscoprire una pillola ormai conosciuta per diminuire i sintomi occasionati da questa infezione?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by @36andfreezing on September 01, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'It's an intense procedure. There's a lot that goes into egg_freezing, before you even get to the part where the eggs are actually frozen. First, you'll have blood drawn to evaluate your ovarian reserve and screen for infectious diseases. You might also have an ultrasound done to see what's up with your overall ovarian function. Then, you'll take synthetic hormones that stimulate your ovaries to grow a cohort of follicles (the cells that house and protect your eggs), and, at the same time, medicine to'.

Photo by @36andfreezing on September 01, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'happens in a doctor's office, with a transvaginal ultrasound aspiration (yes, you can be anesthetized for this procedure). An ultrasound probe is inserted into your vagina to locate the mature follicles. Then your doctor will insert a long, hollow needle through the vaginal canal to the ovaries, then suction is applied to remove the eggs one-by-one. You can remove multiple eggs at a time, which is advisable, since it gives you the best chance of getting a healthy egg that can be fertilized. After the eggs are retrieved. thev're REE via a'.

node.text: #eggfreezing is an intense procedure! So there are lots of things I thought about before I embarked on my #eggfreezingjourney. Everyone’s considerations will be different. I’m 36 now but what with the #covid19 related delays, I’ll be 37 when I go through the procedure. üò¨ eggs can only be stored for 10 years so this gives me until 47 to use them. According to a study I read online, a 34 year old would need to freeze 10 eggs to have a 75% chance of having a live birth ü§∑üèª‍‚ôÄÔ∏èhere’s hoping that all the prep work I’m putting in pays off ü§ûto anyone considering this, I’d say think about your family goals and whether you’d use your eggs if you didn’t meet someone. Think about the initial costs but also the #storagecosts and costs further down the line if you go through #ivf make sure this is something you really want to do. Above all, bear in mind that whilst this is an insurance policy, it isn’t guaranteed to pay out! There is no guarantee that the procedure will be successful or that your eggs will survive and be viable in years to come ü§Øü§Øü§Ø
